{"tid":2387366,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拒區會買口罩 民政轄下建制委員會辦150人講座","createTime":"2021-01-30T09:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T09:36:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c057b0f35a789d1b64e4d9d344fd11b34939ac0a","tid":2387366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:10:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210130/XEAKAQI3MJAULBWMWGNUYZBYWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210130%2FXEAKAQI3MJAULBWMWGNUYZBYWI%2F&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjNWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=3b077633\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210130%2FXEAKAQI3MJAULBWMWGNUYZBYWI%2F&h=a1eb7b12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210130/XEAKAQI3MJAULBWMWGNUYZBYWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n拒區會買口罩 民政轄下建制委員會辦150人講座<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/U7Mcl_bE7NHOC34TFcs3dmxSIFo=/552x311/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LPSNCM7GW5GDTNPE3DOLOZPSZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FU7Mcl_bE7NHOC34TFcs3dmxSIFo%3D%2F552x311%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLPSNCM7GW5GDTNPE3DOLOZPSZU.jpg&h=c3172b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃文萱<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府早前拒絕由民主派掌控的沙田區議會購買口罩給市民，但由當局委任大量建制派的分區委員會，大舉向區議會申請撥款搞過百人的健康講座。沙田區六個分區委員會前日獲批近30萬元撥款，作為舉辦社區健康講座之用。有沙田區議員質疑，民政事務處早前才拒絕區議會申請撥款購買口罩抗疫，如今與分區委員會協辦搞過容許逾百人出席的健康講座，做法是雙重標準。<br />\n<br />\n沙田民政處轄下的六個分區委員會，向區議會申請撥款舉辦的社區健康講座，聲稱要讓區內居民進一步了解抗疫健康衞生資訊，六個分區委員會的申請資料內容大同小異，例如花3.5萬元購買2,500份包括環保袋和毛巾的紀念品、花近4,000元設計及印刷海報，以及花約2,600元為社區幹事支薪等，按各分區委員會預計，每個講座參與人數約150人。沙田區議會前日批出有關撥款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n議員轟雙重標準<br />\n<br />\n沙田區議員公民黨黃文萱批評，早前沙田民政處才以「善用公帑原則」和市面上已有很多口罩為由，拒絕撥款予區議員購買及派發口罩給市民，如今民政處轄下的分區委員會就申請撥款舉辦每個約有150人出席的講座：「之前話善用公帑原則，咁市面上都好多單張啦，仲要用講座，150人，係限聚令嘅75倍！」她認為今次事件凸顯當局雙重標準。<br />\n<br />\n月前沙田區議會衞生及環境委員會，曾一致通過撥款100萬元，作為派發63萬個口罩和六萬多份防疫小冊子予區內居民之用。不過沙田民政處指，考慮到市面的外科口罩供應情況，政府亦通過各區民政處和社署向有需要人士提供防疫物資，故拒絕支付和發還相關活動的開支。"},{"pid":"e2fc2ab64487e147b4b9381dcb7c13029b7cc445","tid":2387366,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:26:27.000Z","msg":"lol"},{"pid":"b76ba03eebdedf7e5fc9b62595861bdca7dd362a","tid":2387366,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f6019c1378348a5ce866fd4d672fca91003f6c8e","tid":2387366,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c0d9207a41a1e447f20ffcd144da4dc127dc9e","tid":2387366,"uid":104425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:28:52.000Z","msg":"蘋果寫清楚啲會好啲？<br />\n唔係幾信班區議員會咁on9批錢俾分區委員會<br />\n佢講到區議會批，好似講到區議員係有份批咁"},{"pid":"fb636362b0940188fdddec0042e5b57b5b9fe857","tid":2387366,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:29:03.000Z","msg":"走狗徐英偉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2903fb9aa8d73fe98aa6c1570f125369f9207e44","tid":2387366,"uid":255105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"不如民政處改名做「資助失業共狗行政處」算啦"},{"pid":"57f1230178ff144a8a29a7c97854c865b29e7b4b","tid":2387366,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:36:00.000Z","msg":"D建制仲係度派緊大公報 日日幾十人排隊拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}